---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="GÆMZCAM - Game Boy Camera Photowalk" description="GÆMZCAM - Game Boy Camera Photowalk" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.video-embed {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.video-embed iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 0;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
			<strong>GÆMZCAM - Game Boy Camera Photowalk</strong>
			<br>
            Tokyo, Japan
            <br>
            2025
			<br>
            <hr>
            <p>I ran a Game Boy camera photowalk as part of <a href="https://gaemz.carrd.co/">GÆMZ Tokyo</a> event. Participants were encouraged to bring their Game Boy hardware and I led everyone on a walking route through Shibuya. Optional photo prompts were provided.</p>

            <p>Over 20 people attended. Many brought Game Boys and Game Boy Colors with an official Game Boy Camera and Nintendo DS and 3DS. Custom hardware versions of Game Boys were also brought. All photos taken were uploaded to a PC and turned into a video.</p>

            <p>Additional film photos taken by Grisha</p>

            <iframe width="100%" height="512" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xVcQ-zURaiE" title="GAEMZCAM" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>


            <img src="/gaemz/gaemz-cam-poster.webp"/>
            <caption>Poster Art created by <a href="https://www.thenomi.com/">Til Nomi</caption>


			<!-- <div style="width: 25%;">
			<img src="/Written-By-a-Human-Not-By-AI-Badge-white@2x.png" alt="Your Image">
			</div> -->

		</div>
	</body>
</html>